720238f-a.text:
Greenwich Street, north from Clarkson Street, showing surface conditions under the Ninth Avenue Elevated. The street car tracks shown are to be removed by the W. P. A. Intersection in the midground is Leroy Street. This location personally verified on 9-26-1940.
June 2, 1937
W. P. A. photo
Five Boroughs Project
